reviews.review_text: there is a fraklin tower in san fansico 8 31  81 was my first show  lv neavda they played moring dew the place went ape shit i drove up from so cal to se the greek  shows  jerry band next week end at the keystones   there a lot gems this night  but franklin tower rang my bell so afther the show a friend  jr  show were the tower was  back to the show china doll stagger lee  wee epic but the moring dew tore my heart out  relized  what a grate song it was it was gen  addmission  so you flot around i think the next  night they drove out a pan head on stage and let it rip im glad i went  it was heaven  some best shows of my life dont pass this up
